    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The hemolysis measurement campaign provided comprehensive data across the full clinical operating envelope, and CFD predictions agree with measurements within the 15% error threshold. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 at all five operating points satisfies the regulatory acceptance criterion. The six non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scoping per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the intended use decision.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
